lead_paragraph: Vin Diesel and Paul Walker reteam for the ultimate chapter of the franchise built on speed Fast&Furious.  Heading back to the streets where it all began, they rejoin Michelle Rodriguez and Jordana Brewster to blast muscle, tuner and exotic cars ac
